# MQTT Sensor Publisher

## Objective
Publish environmental data from an ESP32 to an MQTT broker using JSON messages.

## Components
- ESP32 Dev Module
- DHT22 Sensor
- LED
- 220Ω Resistor

## MQTT Broker
test.mosquitto.org

## Publish Topics
- iitjammu/summer26/abhishek/temperature
- iitjammu/summer26/abhishek/humidity

## Subscribe Topic
- iitjammu/summer26/abhishek/led_control

## JSON Format

Temperature:

{
  "value": 28.5,
  "unit": "C",
  "ts": 1234567890
}

Humidity:

{
  "value": 62,
  "unit": "%",
  "ts": 1234567890
}

## Libraries Used
- PubSubClient
- DHTesp

## Note
The assignment specifies DHT11. Since Wokwi provides DHT22 in the simulation environment, DHT22 was used as a compatible replacement.
